<abstract><t>This document describes SRv6+. SRv6+ is a Segment Routing (SR) solution that leverages IPv6.  It supports a wide variety of use- cases while remaining in strict compliance with IPv6 specifications. SRv6+ is optimized for ASIC-based forwarding devices that operate at high data rates.</t></abstract>

